  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">\"Endless sunshine, golden sand beaches, and vibrant hues bursting everywhere&mdash;summer's here! Lynae's favorite season, hands down! Hm? The heatwave sapped your energy? Why not pop open another ice-cold soda? (&cap;^o^)&sup;━☆ﾟ.*･\"</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">Lynae's Deluxe Outfit \"Peppermint\" will become available once Version 3.5 goes live. Get a sneak peek now!</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"3\" data-line=\"true\">✦How to Obtain✦</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"4\" data-line=\"true\">Lynae's Deluxe Outfit \"Peppermint\" will be permanently available in the Store once Version 3.5 goes live.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\">Purchase the Outfit during Version 3.5 at a discount price of 1,980 Lunites. After Version 3.5 ends, the price will return to 2,480 Lunites.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/kaj7vb0lms4nysl0rd-1782901878232.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/fo28z7asgd6st5vkvu-1782901918912.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/rkmjayjoggpo2fmot2-1782902065898.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/2r9p5bf01mo9tlrgvc-1782901951985.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/swcptncqjorkwqwmc8-1782901981547.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/um5wzpjyj819gjwr0m-1782901995014.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
